## ğŸ› ï¸ API Endpoints

### ğŸ” Auth Routes (`/api/auth`)
- `POST /register` â†’ Register with `@surveillance.in` email
- `POST /login` â†’ Login and receive JWT token

### ğŸ“Š Dashboard Route (`/api/dashboard`)
- `GET /` â†’ Protected route (JWT required)

### ğŸ“¹ Stream Routes (Flask backend)
- `GET /video_feed` â†’ Live camera feed with detection
- `POST /stop` â†’ Stops streaming and saves the video

